text: Keshav Prasad Pokharel (Nepali: केशवप्रसाद पोखरेल) is Nepalese politician and member of the Bagmati Provincial Assembly who was elected form Kathmandu 9 (B). He is currently serving as Minister for Agriculture and Livestock Development of Bagmti Province in Jamkattel cabinet. == References == Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Communist Party of Nepal (Unified Marxist–Leninist) politicians
